FBIS3-54668 "drsov001_v_94001" FBIS-SOV-94-001 Document Type:Daily Report 3 Jan 1994 Lithuania Brazauskas Chairs Defense Council Session PM2912171193 Moscow KRASNAYA ZVEZDA in Russian 30 Dec 93 p 1 PM2912171193 Moscow KRASNAYA ZVEZDA Language: Russian Article Type:BFN [Report by Captain First Rank Valeriy Gromak: "If There Were a Doctrine, the Ministry Would Follow"] [Text] A session of the Defense Council has been held in Vilnius. It was chaired by Lithuanian President Algirdas Brazauskas. The session discussed Lithuania's military doctrine. In addition it examined avenues for reorganizing the structure of the Ministry of National Defense.
